version_description: The lyrics have not been officially released, and it's hard to tell what he's singing, so here is the best interpretation I could find. The recording was started after the song begun, so the first verse appears to be cut off.
Alternate version (Dylan's acoustic demo released on "The Bootleg Series Vol. 03"): different key and time signature / complete chords and lyrics.
All new version based on the studio version of the song on "The Bootleg Series Volume 2.".
Complete chords and lyrics / tip for novice players to avoid barre chords.
This is a chart for the SLOW version from Plant Waves. It includes measure markers, changes in time signature, correct chords, and the instrumental outro.
Chords for the acoustic demo recorded in June 1973, First released on "Biograph", now on "Side Tracks".

This is from the Complete Basement Tapes, performed with the band. Bob forgets the lyrics of the start of Verse 2, and just improvises garbled sound, but I have replaced it with the original song lyrics.
Complete chords and lyrics / open-D tuning/ voicings.
This is the Freewheelin’ album version which uses different chords to the Nashville Skyline recording with Johnny Cash.

song_name: Goin Down The Road Feeling Bad
version_description: As recorded on The Basement Tapes Complete. The song is actually played in G#, but for simplicity I have transposed it to G, to be played with a Capo 1, or with barre chords.
